title: IAA Tonight | Ranking the Top 10 QB's and Where's Donovan Mitchell's Next Destination?
description: ESPN put out a list ranking the top 10 QB's and RB's for the upcoming 2022 season, but Brandon Marshall, Adam 'Pacman' Jones, and Antoine Walker decided to create their own due to some glaring omissions. Plus, Pacman was on vacation and ran into Utah Jazz star G Donovan Mitchell, who may not be there for much longer after some of the moves they've made this offseason.
author: smanderville@houseofathlete.com (Brandon Marshall, Adam 'Pacman' Jones, Antoine Walker)
